---
title: "outbound-result.ts"
---

## High-level description
This TypeScript file defines interfaces for handling responses from various outbound operations in the Carequality IHE Gateway. It provides structured types for patient discovery, document query, and document retrieval responses, extending a base result domain.

## Code Structure
The file defines four interfaces: one base interface (`BaseResultDomain`) and three specific interfaces that extend it (`OutboundPatientDiscoveryRespTableEntry`, `OutboundDocumentQueryRespTableEntry`, and `OutboundDocumentRetrievalRespTableEntry`). Each specific interface corresponds to a different type of outbound operation response.

## References
The code imports response types from the "@metriport/ihe-gateway-sdk" package, which are used in the `data` field of the specific interfaces.

## Symbols

### `BaseResultDomain`
#### Description
This interface defines the common properties for all outbound operation responses.

#### Inputs
| Name | Type | Description |
|:-----|:-----|:------------|
| requestId | string | Unique identifier for the request |
| status | string | Status of the request |
| createdAt | Date | Timestamp of when the result was created |

### `OutboundPatientDiscoveryRespTableEntry`
#### Description
This interface extends `BaseResultDomain` and adds a `data` field specific to patient discovery responses.

#### Inputs
| Name | Type | Description |
|:-----|:-----|:------------|
| data | IHEOutboundPatientDiscoveryResp | Patient discovery response data |

### `OutboundDocumentQueryRespTableEntry`
#### Description
This interface extends `BaseResultDomain` and adds a `data` field specific to document query responses.

#### Inputs
| Name | Type | Description |
|:-----|:-----|:------------|
| data | IHEOutboundDocumentQueryResp | Document query response data |

### `OutboundDocumentRetrievalRespTableEntry`
#### Description
This interface extends `BaseResultDomain` and adds a `data` field specific to document retrieval responses.

#### Inputs
| Name | Type | Description |
|:-----|:-----|:------------|
| data | IHEOutboundDocumentRetrievalResp | Document retrieval response data |

## Dependencies
| Dependency | Purpose |
|:-----------|:--------|
| @metriport/ihe-gateway-sdk | Provides types for IHE Gateway response data |

This file serves as a type definition module for handling various outbound operation responses in the Carequality IHE Gateway context. It provides a structured way to represent and work with these responses, ensuring type safety and consistency across the application when dealing with patient discovery, document query, and document retrieval operations.
